<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 16:09:58 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>被释放的以色列人质在电视采访中描述哈马斯视频是如何制作的</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-13/ty-article/.premium/released-israeli-hostage-describes-how-gaza-videos-were-made-in-tv-interview/0000018f-7250-d7ad-abdf-f65ea34d0000</link><description>梅拉夫·塔尔告诉第 12 频道新闻，当她与其他人一起被巴勒斯坦伊斯兰圣战组织扣押时，拍摄了几个小时的镜头，其中大部分未公开</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 15:36:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-13/ty-article/.premium/released-israeli-hostage-describes-how-gaza-videos-were-made-in-tv-interview/0000018f-7250-d7ad-abdf-f65ea34d0000</guid></item><item><title>56年前，一艘以色列潜艇失踪。船上有我的邻居阿里克</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-13/ty-article-magazine/.premium/56-years-ago-an-israeli-submarine-disappeared-on-board-was-my-neighbor-arik/0000018f-71d0-d7ad-abdf-f5de0d7d0000</link><description>我的邻居 Arik Feingold 与其他达喀尔船员一起失踪时年仅 22 岁。以色列阵亡士兵纪念碑之间的旅程揭示了我们感知死亡、记忆和丧亲之痛的方式</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 14:05:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-13/ty-article-magazine/.premium/56-years-ago-an-israeli-submarine-disappeared-on-board-was-my-neighbor-arik/0000018f-71d0-d7ad-abdf-f5de0d7d0000</guid></item><item><title>今年独立日，以色列分裂成两个互不相容的犹太国家</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-13/ty-article/.premium/this-independence-day-israel-has-split-into-two-incompatible-jewish-states/0000018f-71b9-d802-addf-73fb3b800000</link><description>10 月 7 日的灾难和以色列建国 76 周年纪念日的结合可能会暂时平息政治辩论，但它无法掩盖现实：现在这里有两个国家——以色列和犹太——对国家应该是什么样的愿景有着截然不同的看法</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 12:45:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-13/ty-article/.premium/this-independence-day-israel-has-split-into-two-incompatible-jewish-states/0000018f-71b9-d802-addf-73fb3b800000</guid></item><item><title>首先，以色列警方拒绝允许在特拉维夫大学门口举行灾难日活动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-13/ty-article/.premium/in-first-israel-police-refuse-to-permit-nakba-day-event-at-gate-of-tel-aviv-university/0000018f-71aa-d70d-a78f-79aa8e8b0000</link><description>活动组织者被口头告知这一决定，但没有收到正式原因。一名组织者表示，“他们提出让我们在一个封闭的大厅或阿拉伯城市举行示威”</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 12:05:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-13/ty-article/.premium/in-first-israel-police-refuse-to-permit-nakba-day-event-at-gate-of-tel-aviv-university/0000018f-71aa-d70d-a78f-79aa8e8b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列与埃及的裂痕可能为加沙巴勒斯坦权力机构创造未来</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-13/ty-article/.premium/israels-rift-with-egypt-could-create-a-future-for-the-palestinian-authority-in-gaza/0000018f-70c0-d7ad-abdf-f4de8b530000</link><description>埃及在占领拉法过境点后决定停止与以色列协调，这表明开罗愿意采取严厉措施。但为了确保巴勒斯坦权力机构在加沙的“事后”计划得以实施，以色列必须从斯莫特里奇手中接过钥匙，并面对必要的政治变革</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 11:55:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-13/ty-article/.premium/israels-rift-with-egypt-could-create-a-future-for-the-palestinian-authority-in-gaza/0000018f-70c0-d7ad-abdf-f4de8b530000</guid></item><item><title>基布兹曾经是以色列的未来。 10月7日之后可能会再次出现</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-13/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-kibbutz-was-once-the-future-of-israel-after-october-7-it-could-be-once-again/0000018f-70ff-db4b-a5ef-79ff7c1a0000</link><description>哈马斯袭击后，多年来一直是全国性出气筒并成为脱节和特权象征的基布兹正在重返以色列文化话语的中心</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 11:45:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-13/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-kibbutz-was-once-the-future-of-israel-after-october-7-it-could-be-once-again/0000018f-70ff-db4b-a5ef-79ff7c1a0000</guid></item><item><title>有人一直住在这里直到 1948 年：在以色列建立之前，巴勒斯坦人就住在海法</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-05-13/ty-article-magazine/.premium/someone-lived-here-until-1948-palestinian-lives-in-haifa-before-israel-was-established/0000018f-70ff-db4b-a5ef-79ff4be00000</link><description>以色列北部城市海法长期以来一直被誉为阿拉伯-犹太混合城市。但是，对以色列建立之前居住在那里的巴勒斯坦人的生活进行的追踪揭示了更详细的现实。 “口头证词揭示了新闻中未报道的事情”</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 10:28:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-05-13/ty-article-magazine/.premium/someone-lived-here-until-1948-palestinian-lives-in-haifa-before-israel-was-established/0000018f-70ff-db4b-a5ef-79ff4be00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列庆祝前所未有的阵亡将士纪念日，家人对内塔尼亚胡政府感到愤怒</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-13/ty-article/israel-commemorates-memorial-day-amid-october-7-gaza-war-siren-to-sound-at-11-a-m/0000018f-7085-d7ad-abdf-f49f7cc50000</link><description>死者家属和人质家属分别举行活动和抗议活动，其中一些人试图阻止政府部长参加仪式。晚上 8 点，阵亡将士纪念日将结束，独立日活动将开始</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 06:03:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-13/ty-article/israel-commemorates-memorial-day-amid-october-7-gaza-war-siren-to-sound-at-11-a-m/0000018f-7085-d7ad-abdf-f49f7cc50000</guid></item><item><title>在贱民阵营深处，以色列人继续为一场看不到尽头的战争付出巨大代价</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-13/ty-article/.premium/as-the-iccs-threat-looms-israel-is-hanging-on-by-its-fingernails/0000018f-6e4a-d336-abdf-fedf3e500000</link><description>以色列有史以来最长的消耗战仍在继续，如果没有有意识的政策决定，它可能会逐渐在加沙建立军政府，而内塔尼亚胡坚持拉法行动却损害了其国际地位</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 03:00:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-13/ty-article/.premium/as-the-iccs-threat-looms-israel-is-hanging-on-by-its-fingernails/0000018f-6e4a-d336-abdf-fedf3e500000</guid></item><item><title>过去两天，五名士兵和国防部承包商在加沙地带受伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-13/ty-article-live/blinken-speaks-to-gallant-reaffirms-u-s-opposition-to-rafah-ground-operation/0000018f-6faa-d7ad-abdf-ffbe26780000</link><description>埃尔多安：1,000 多名哈马斯成员在土耳其医院接受治疗 ■ 四名以色列抗议者因拦截前往加沙的人道主义援助车队而被捕，并对援助卡车造成损坏 ■ 以色列国防军：两架无人机在以色列北部爆炸；两架无人机在以色列北部爆炸。没有人员伤亡报道 ■ 加沙边境社区火箭警报响起 ■ 哈马斯武装派别表示，他们与看守四名以色列人质的武装分子失去了联系</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 02:04:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-13/ty-article-live/blinken-speaks-to-gallant-reaffirms-u-s-opposition-to-rafah-ground-operation/0000018f-6faa-d7ad-abdf-ffbe26780000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人不同意内塔尼亚胡政府的独立日表演</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-05-12/ty-article/.highlight/how-israelis-are-marking-memorial-and-independence-days/0000018f-6da6-d336-abdf-fff7d7820000</link><description>如果说以色列阵亡将士纪念日和独立日之间的过渡总是让人感觉有点尴尬，那么今年的仪式无疑是不合适和不合适的。两个替代仪式可能表明越来越多的以色列人不会参加这场庄严的表演</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 May 2024 19:48:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-05-12/ty-article/.highlight/how-israelis-are-marking-memorial-and-independence-days/0000018f-6da6-d336-abdf-fff7d7820000</guid></item><item><title>埃及将加入南非国际法院针对以色列的案件；以色列高级官员：“国家间关系再创新低”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-12/ty-article/.premium/egypt-to-join-south-africas-icj-case-against-israel-after-rafah-operation/0000018f-6d85-d336-abdf-ffd7358b0000</link><description>埃及的声明预计不会对国际法院的法律程序产生实质性影响，但反映出两国关系新低。以色列消息人士担心，国际法院可能会对以色列发布新的命令，因为拉法的行动对获得人道主义援助产生了重大影响</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 May 2024 16:50:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-12/ty-article/.premium/egypt-to-join-south-africas-icj-case-against-israel-after-rafah-operation/0000018f-6d85-d336-abdf-ffd7358b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 219 天：据报道真主党将从边境撤出大部分部队</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-12/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-219-hezbollah-to-reportedly-withdraw-most-forces-from-border/0000018f-6da0-d336-abdf-fff76a0c0000</link><description>布林肯：以色列没有向美国展示阻止哈马斯在加沙地区重建存在的“可信计划” 以色列国防军已撤离 ■ 据报道，拜登政府向以色列提供了有关哈马斯领导人的情报，以换取避免拉法行动 ■ 埃及宣布加入南方联盟非洲在国际法院向以色列请愿 ■ 据报道，真主党计划逐步从边境撤出大部分战斗人员 ■ 战争进入 219 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 May 2024 16:33:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-12/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-219-hezbollah-to-reportedly-withdraw-most-forces-from-border/0000018f-6da0-d336-abdf-fff76a0c0000</guid></item><item><title>10 月 7 日后几天，以色列士兵在与哈马斯作战时自杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-12/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-israeli-soldiers-who-took-their-own-lives-while-fighting-hamas-days-after-october-7/0000018f-6c88-d0ae-adef-eddded4f0000</link><description>自战争开始以来，已有十名军官和士兵自杀身亡，其中一些军官和士兵自杀身亡，而以色列与加沙边境的战斗仍在激烈进行。与亲属和专业人士的对话表明，他们在大屠杀现场所看到的一切摧毁了他们的灵魂</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 May 2024 16:06:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-12/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-israeli-soldiers-who-took-their-own-lives-while-fighting-hamas-days-after-october-7/0000018f-6c88-d0ae-adef-eddded4f0000</guid></item><item><title>为什么以色列将军现在公开通报反对内塔尼亚胡的情况</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-12/ty-article/.premium/why-israels-generals-are-now-openly-briefing-against-netanyahu/0000018f-6d15-d8c9-a3cf-6d5deb5b0000</link><description>以色列军事指挥官本应在 10 月份进入加沙之前就哈马斯事件后第二天缺乏战略问题与内塔尼亚胡对质。现在，他们指责他浪费了他们的战术成果也许是正确的，但他们也必须承担一些责任</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 May 2024 15:27:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-12/ty-article/.premium/why-israels-generals-are-now-openly-briefing-against-netanyahu/0000018f-6d15-d8c9-a3cf-6d5deb5b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队正式宣布在加沙北部贾巴利亚开始行动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-12/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-officially-announces-start-of-operation-in-northern-gazas-jabalya/0000018f-6d0f-d8c9-a3cf-6d4fb8210000</link><description>以色列国防军宣布他们已经击败了哈马斯在该地区的能力几个月后，军队表示哈马斯已经返回贾巴利亚，并呼吁居民在新的战斗之前撤离到加沙城</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 May 2024 14:43:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-12/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-officially-announces-start-of-operation-in-northern-gazas-jabalya/0000018f-6d0f-d8c9-a3cf-6d4fb8210000</guid></item><item><title>米哈尔 (Michal) 于 10 月 7 日失去了儿子，纳吉拉 (Najlaa) 在加沙埋葬了她的兄弟。他们一起寻找不同的未来</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-12/ty-article-magazine/.premium/michal-lost-her-son-najalaah-buried-her-brother-together-they-seek-a-different-future/0000018f-6c9b-de93-a1af-7c9b51dd0000</link><description>自 10 月 7 日以来，许多失去亲人的以色列人和巴勒斯坦人选择参加“父母圈-家庭论坛”。其中六人告诉《国土报》，他们选择站在一起，但周围社会的支持很少</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 May 2024 14:34:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-12/ty-article-magazine/.premium/michal-lost-her-son-najalaah-buried-her-brother-together-they-seek-a-different-future/0000018f-6c9b-de93-a1af-7c9b51dd0000</guid></item><item><title>“以色列-巴勒斯坦阵亡将士纪念日仪式展示了加沙战争后的第二天会是什么样子”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-05-12/ty-article-podcast/israeli-palestinian-memorial-shows-what-the-day-after-the-gaza-war-could-look-like/0000018f-6ca5-d284-adaf-7cfd64740000</link><description></description><pubDate>Sun, 12 May 2024 13:53:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-05-12/ty-article-podcast/israeli-palestinian-memorial-shows-what-the-day-after-the-gaza-war-could-look-like/0000018f-6ca5-d284-adaf-7cfd64740000</guid></item><item><title>身份不明的肇事者纵火焚烧约旦河西岸的巴勒斯坦空房子</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-12/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-empty-house-in-west-bank-set-on-fire-by-unknown-perpetrators/0000018f-6cac-d5b5-a18f-efecabef0000</link><description>房子的墙壁上贴满了标语：“Tag mehir [“价格标签”]——本雅明去世 30 天”，标志着居住在附近定居点的 14 岁以色列男孩本雅明·阿希梅尔 (Binyamin Ahimeir) 被谋杀 30 天。</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 May 2024 13:51:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-12/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-empty-house-in-west-bank-set-on-fire-by-unknown-perpetrators/0000018f-6cac-d5b5-a18f-efecabef0000</guid></item><item><title>拜登并没有背弃以色列。但内塔尼亚胡已经</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-12/ty-article/.premium/biden-has-not-turned-his-back-on-israel-but-netanyahu-has/0000018f-6bea-d4be-abcf-6bef0bd80000</link><description>几乎从加沙战争一开始，内塔尼亚胡政府就不仅与哈马斯对抗，还与美国总统对抗。将拜登推向崩溃可能会对本已紧张的美以关系造成不可挽回的损害</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 May 2024 13:01:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-12/ty-article/.premium/biden-has-not-turned-his-back-on-israel-but-netanyahu-has/0000018f-6bea-d4be-abcf-6bef0bd80000</guid></item></channel></rss>